{
  "id": "ex_technical_6e4e59bb",
  "intent": "Execute a magnetic bead-based nucleic acid extraction protocol for 48 samples using NucleoMag reagents. Add 20\u00b5L magnetic beads and 600\u00b5L binding buffer to 400\u00b5L sample volumes, mix 20 times, incubate on magnetic module for 5 minutes at 5.5mm height. Perform three sequential washes: 600\u00b5L NPW3 buffer, 600\u00b5L NPW4 buffer, and 600\u00b5L 80% ethanol with 15-20 mixing cycles each, followed by 2-minute magnetic separations. Air dry for 40 minutes, then elute in 100\u00b5L NPE5 buffer with 20 mixing cycles and 5-minute magnetic separation before transferring to clean plate.",
